 remains smelling as if it was new.","extra_text":"- Jesus R."}},"review_XzwBtX":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_text":"\"... if you care about sustainable production.\"","reviewer_name":"I will be using this shirt as my go-to for all my outdoor activities (mostly hiking\/backpacking) this year. For the price I feel like this is a pretty good buy if you're looking for something a little nicer than a run-of-the-mill merino shirt or if you care about sustainable production.","extra_text":"- Sean C."}},"review_B9yAiV":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_text":"\"Warm, soft, cosy - great for Montana winters.\"","reviewer_name":"I love these Alpaca Wool Sweatpants. Warm, soft, cosy, great for Montana winters. I'm so short I tuck the ankle bands up under the legs, which helps keep my ever-cold ankles warm. They also look great-- trim but not light, and the on-seam pockets don't budge!","extra_text":"- Kate"}},"review_XHGhfn":{"type":"review","settings":{"review_text":"\"The beanie that makes you hate your other beanies.\"","reviewer_name":"Soft beyond what I can describe. When I sweat it wicks it straight to the surface and doesn’t feel damp. I ended up getting a few because I don’t ever want to not be able to find one when my head is cold.","extra_text":"- Ethan"}}},"block_order":["review_8EV8Gm","review_wXKxHb","review_ebTVgj","review_XzwBtX","review_B9yAiV","review_XHGhfn"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC09327-Edit-1.jpg"}},"pagefly-home":{"type":"pagefly-home","disabled":true,"settings":{}}},"order":["image_with_text_overlay_6jKKUK","custom3product_zwWaYd","image_with_text_Tp7bG6","text_with_icons_bWMJ7L","multicolumn_VK8gkq","rich_text_EdHJ9c","text_with_icons_rjD7GM","image_with_review_slider_qrtCVL","pagefly-home"]}